#: subscribe.php:47
msgid ""
"Subscribe - Newsletter Opt-In for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be "
"active."
msgstr ""
"Suscríbase: la suscripción al boletín informativo para WooCommerce requiere "
"que WooCommerce esté activo."
